WEBVTT

00:00:26.359 --> 00:00:29.362
Your Majesty, Prince Iksang has arrived.

00:00:31.698 --> 00:00:33.408
Has his son come as well?

00:00:34.617 --> 00:00:35.702
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:00:38.288 --> 00:00:40.457
How is Prince Yeongan's health?

00:00:40.540 --> 00:00:41.958
There has been no improvement,

00:00:42.542 --> 00:00:45.003
So he will not be able to attend at this time.

00:00:52.552 --> 00:00:54.763
-You may leave. -Yes.

00:00:58.975 --> 00:01:02.604
It seems that Gu-cheon has failed his part, Your Majesty.

00:01:05.398 --> 00:01:07.150
I've heard people say

00:01:08.109 --> 00:01:11.446
The reason I am able to sit on this throne is due to spirits.

00:01:12.405 --> 00:01:13.990
Now they mock me,

00:01:15.366 --> 00:01:19.287
Saying that my position will be threatened because of spirits.

00:01:21.164 --> 00:01:23.208
Which do you believe to be true?

00:01:39.224 --> 00:01:42.227
We will know which one when we get there.

00:01:45.855 --> 00:01:49.943
Kneel before the honored guest, straighten yourself,

00:01:50.026 --> 00:01:53.404
And perform the four ceremonial bows.

00:01:58.910 --> 00:02:00.537
Bow.

00:02:01.079 --> 00:02:03.373
Straighten.

00:02:03.456 --> 00:02:05.542
Bow.

00:02:06.251 --> 00:02:08.795
Straighten.

00:02:09.337 --> 00:02:11.548
Bow.

00:02:11.631 --> 00:02:14.050
Straighten.

00:02:23.977 --> 00:02:27.063
Next, the Crown Prince would present a ceremonial drink,

00:02:27.147 --> 00:02:29.357
Praying for your long life without illness.

00:02:29.858 --> 00:02:33.444
However, as the seat is vacant, I suggest you omit it.

00:02:33.528 --> 00:02:34.988
No. That's enough.

00:02:37.031 --> 00:02:38.950
This tired and old body

00:02:39.617 --> 00:02:43.037
Cannot be certain any longer of another birthday to come.

00:02:44.038 --> 00:02:47.041
And what do you think of that, Your Majesty?

00:02:51.129 --> 00:02:53.506
Then you must do as you wish, Mother.

00:03:04.100 --> 00:03:07.687
Prince Iksang's eldest son, will you step forward right now?

00:03:08.271 --> 00:03:10.356
Prince Iksang, congratulations.

00:03:40.136 --> 00:03:42.805
This is the drink presented by Prince Inha.

00:03:43.389 --> 00:03:46.935
Your Royal Highness, I pray for your well-being.

00:04:07.247 --> 00:04:08.581
What is happening?

00:04:56.296 --> 00:04:58.715
I can tell that something has arrived here.

00:05:27.869 --> 00:05:28.786
All right.

00:05:30.621 --> 00:05:33.291
I knew that if I drove you far enough,

00:05:34.083 --> 00:05:36.711
You would come to me with that resentment.

00:05:38.296 --> 00:05:39.505
Now,

00:05:40.506 --> 00:05:42.050
What will you do?

00:06:02.570 --> 00:06:03.946
Gu-cheon!

00:06:15.833 --> 00:06:17.377
Get a hold of yourself!

00:06:18.836 --> 00:06:20.088
You'll become an ak-gwi.

00:06:20.171 --> 00:06:22.340
If you kill, that's what's going to happen to you.

00:06:27.512 --> 00:06:29.680
You said that becoming an ak-gwi after death

00:06:30.640 --> 00:06:32.558
Was what you feared more than anything.

00:06:38.314 --> 00:06:39.315
Gu-cheon!

00:06:40.191 --> 00:06:42.568
Your mother's death was not your fault. You must believe that.

00:06:48.241 --> 00:06:50.618
You were possessed by the gwi-mae.

00:06:52.328 --> 00:06:54.497
If you still won't trust me,

00:06:55.373 --> 00:06:57.166
Then I'll get to the bottom of this.

00:06:58.251 --> 00:06:59.627
The second we can leave the palace,

00:06:59.710 --> 00:07:01.879
I will go find your mother's grave so we can uncover the

00:07:10.972 --> 00:07:12.014
Please, Gu-cheon.

00:07:13.474 --> 00:07:15.852
Let us make it out of the palace alive.

00:08:00.104 --> 00:08:05.026
THE EAST PALACE

00:08:22.084 --> 00:08:23.336
What is wrong with him?

00:08:23.836 --> 00:08:26.506
What happened to him? Come on. Wake up!

00:08:27.006 --> 00:08:28.674
Send for the physician!

00:08:28.758 --> 00:08:30.468
Summon the physician now!

00:08:30.968 --> 00:08:32.136
Your Majesty.

00:08:36.474 --> 00:08:38.726
This child is a little flawed.

00:08:43.272 --> 00:08:46.192
You must be disappointed with what you're observing, Mother.

00:08:47.860 --> 00:08:49.695
In such a frail state,

00:08:50.238 --> 00:08:54.242
How could he ever endure the palace's energy?

00:08:58.454 --> 00:09:02.041
I must say you need improving when reading others, Mother.

00:09:03.793 --> 00:09:05.920
Resume the banquet at once.

00:09:06.003 --> 00:09:08.548
Carry on the music!

00:09:08.631 --> 00:09:11.550
What are you standing around for? Attend to Prince Inha at once!

00:09:49.130 --> 00:09:50.506
No, no.

00:10:01.976 --> 00:10:02.977
Princess.

00:10:03.894 --> 00:10:04.937
Princess!

00:10:27.376 --> 00:10:28.544
Have you lost your mind?

00:10:29.378 --> 00:10:31.380
I told you to never set foot in there.

00:10:32.381 --> 00:10:34.300
You've never listened to me once.

00:10:35.593 --> 00:10:37.261
I saved you, and this is the thanks I get.

00:10:38.304 --> 00:10:42.433
Am I supposed to do nothing and just stand by and watch you become a gwi-sin?

00:10:42.516 --> 00:10:44.268
You are never to do something like that again,

00:10:44.352 --> 00:10:46.103
Whether I am a spirit or not.

00:10:47.396 --> 00:10:50.524
I never want to see someone die because of me again.

00:11:06.749 --> 00:11:08.042
I will never do it again

00:11:09.085 --> 00:11:10.711
If you truly cannot bear it.

00:11:12.171 --> 00:11:13.339
I, too,

00:11:14.965 --> 00:11:17.134
Cannot convince myself to go in again.

00:11:17.927 --> 00:11:19.512
I was terrified.

00:11:22.890 --> 00:11:24.600
It must have been very difficult for you,

00:11:26.519 --> 00:11:28.479
Having spent all that time in there.

00:12:13.607 --> 00:12:15.609
Everyone who carries the King's blood is mad.

00:12:15.693 --> 00:12:18.028
There are no such things as spirits.

00:12:19.196 --> 00:12:20.239
Mother.

00:12:20.740 --> 00:12:22.575
There are no spirits.

00:12:24.452 --> 00:12:25.995
There are no spirits.

00:12:28.247 --> 00:12:29.373
Mother?

00:12:31.125 --> 00:12:33.252
Your father is the palace entity.

00:12:58.569 --> 00:12:59.403
How are you?

00:13:04.450 --> 00:13:06.952
What are you doing out there?

00:13:07.036 --> 00:13:09.246
How is it? Your fever?

00:13:11.081 --> 00:13:13.209
Why would you open the window without asking?

00:13:16.128 --> 00:13:17.922
At least you still have your temper.

00:13:25.137 --> 00:13:26.639
Miss Saeng-gang, you're awake!

00:13:27.681 --> 00:13:29.183
How are you feeling now?

00:13:29.683 --> 00:13:31.852
What in the world is going on?

00:13:34.688 --> 00:13:35.898
I thought Gu-cheon was dead.

00:13:35.981 --> 00:13:37.942
Now he's talking to you and walking around.

00:13:38.025 --> 00:13:40.861
And you, who are perfectly fine, slept for three days and nights.

00:13:40.945 --> 00:13:42.863
I mean, you basically slept like the dead.

00:13:43.447 --> 00:13:44.657
It was three days?

00:13:44.740 --> 00:13:46.492
Yes! Have this first.

00:13:46.575 --> 00:13:49.453
I had to beg the female royal physician to brew this medicine,

00:13:49.537 --> 00:13:51.872
And I snuck some rice cakes to bring to you here.

00:13:51.956 --> 00:13:54.250
You haven't eaten one thing for three days.

00:13:55.084 --> 00:13:56.752
Here, please have these.

00:13:58.295 --> 00:13:59.547
I appreciate it.

00:14:08.055 --> 00:14:10.933
But, um, why did you bring me so many rice cakes?

00:14:12.059 --> 00:14:13.602
It's Gu-cheon.

00:14:13.686 --> 00:14:16.063
I brought some for him also.

00:14:16.146 --> 00:14:17.273
But he just left.

00:14:17.356 --> 00:14:20.192
He must have terrible luck with food. Is he not even hungry?

00:14:20.276 --> 00:14:21.735
He has not eaten for three days.

00:14:26.532 --> 00:14:27.408
Mmm.

00:14:36.584 --> 00:14:39.587
After three days without food, it tastes better.

00:14:40.838 --> 00:14:41.755
Do you want some?

00:14:45.259 --> 00:14:47.011
I don't have an appetite.

00:14:47.094 --> 00:14:48.554
Please help yourself.

00:14:52.016 --> 00:14:53.225
You should eat too.

00:14:55.144 --> 00:14:56.604
You cannot work without it.

00:14:57.563 --> 00:14:59.523
I found something at the guard's house.

00:15:00.441 --> 00:15:02.443
I will handle all of that.

00:15:02.526 --> 00:15:04.987
You needn't be concerned, Your Highness.

00:15:05.821 --> 00:15:07.031
"Your Highness"?

00:15:08.616 --> 00:15:09.450
What?

00:15:10.242 --> 00:15:11.076
What?

00:15:14.705 --> 00:15:15.956
You have changed somehow.

00:15:28.010 --> 00:15:29.219
So, anyway,

00:15:30.012 --> 00:15:32.097
Tell me what you have found at the house.

00:15:33.807 --> 00:15:37.311
I found what the Favored Court Lady made for the child she was carrying.

00:15:41.357 --> 00:15:43.776
Do you think this could ease her resentment?

00:15:45.361 --> 00:15:49.698
It might be possible, but the preparation will be complicated.

00:15:50.407 --> 00:15:52.284
Her spirit is not ordinary.

00:15:53.160 --> 00:15:55.788
She killed people for 30 years as a won-gwi.

00:15:57.957 --> 00:16:01.210
Oh! The lightning-struck jujube wood. Where did you get that?

00:16:02.169 --> 00:16:05.839
Ah! The jujube tree inside the palace was struck by lightning.

00:16:06.507 --> 00:16:08.634
-Oh. -Was that branch helpful at all?

00:16:10.386 --> 00:16:13.722
It helped a great deal having that wood, and it will continue to help.

00:16:14.223 --> 00:16:15.516
Well,

00:16:16.266 --> 00:16:18.686
I believe I have helped in more ways than one.

00:16:19.186 --> 00:16:21.313
The least you could do is say thank you.

00:16:21.397 --> 00:16:25.526
You know, the second you brag, it makes all of your goodwill disappear?

00:16:25.609 --> 00:16:27.569
And how is that bragging?

00:16:27.653 --> 00:16:29.947
It is simply the praise I am owed.

00:16:30.489 --> 00:16:32.491
I nearly died dealing with your family's mess,

00:16:32.574 --> 00:16:34.034
And you want my thanks and praise?

00:16:34.827 --> 00:16:36.412
What? You want recognition that badly?

00:16:41.834 --> 00:16:42.876
Forget it.

00:16:44.211 --> 00:16:46.755
Fine. I do not need your thanks.

00:16:46.839 --> 00:16:48.882
But you should be thanking the Ggeomeoksali.

00:16:50.342 --> 00:16:52.803
The gwi-mae had you in the well, and it saved you.

00:16:53.971 --> 00:16:54.888
That saved me?

00:16:54.972 --> 00:16:57.599
I did wonder why I had not seen it roaming around here.

00:16:57.683 --> 00:16:59.768
It fell into the well while helping fight the gwi-mae.

00:17:00.602 --> 00:17:01.854
How sad.

00:17:01.937 --> 00:17:03.147
Good riddance.

00:17:06.442 --> 00:17:07.860
Don't be cold about it!

00:17:07.943 --> 00:17:11.739
I don't make stupid decisions like getting attached to it like you do.

00:17:12.239 --> 00:17:14.867
Let's just focus on the pond spirit and how to get rid of it.

00:17:27.087 --> 00:17:28.464
Is something wrong?

00:17:28.547 --> 00:17:29.506
The truth is

00:17:34.803 --> 00:17:38.891
When I crossed over to the other side, I came face-to-face with the pond spirit.

00:17:41.477 --> 00:17:44.229
It clawed my back and drained my spiritual energy.

00:17:45.773 --> 00:17:48.776
But I was able to come back because you pulled the rope just in time.

00:17:52.112 --> 00:17:53.363
It clawed you?

00:18:03.874 --> 00:18:05.042
What's the matter?

00:18:08.504 --> 00:18:09.421
Uh

00:18:12.382 --> 00:18:14.843
The spirit that consumed your soul down there

00:18:17.513 --> 00:18:19.598
Has likely begun to regain its strength from it.

00:18:20.808 --> 00:18:24.770
The curse that had briefly weakened will grow stronger again.

00:18:25.646 --> 00:18:26.814
Your Majesty.

00:18:27.439 --> 00:18:29.483
The royal physician attending Prince Yeongan

00:18:29.566 --> 00:18:32.778
Says you must prepare yourself for what is to come.

00:18:45.791 --> 00:18:46.959
Why?

00:18:57.344 --> 00:19:01.723
Is confronting the spirit impulsively like this truly wise?

00:19:02.975 --> 00:19:06.812
I believe Prince Yeongan won't make it through the night, most likely.

00:19:07.312 --> 00:19:10.357
He's reached his limit after enduring the curse for so long.

00:19:11.692 --> 00:19:13.360
We cannot waste more time.

00:19:17.364 --> 00:19:18.574
Sh!

00:19:20.534 --> 00:19:21.618
Can you hear it?

00:19:22.244 --> 00:19:23.245
That sound?

00:19:38.927 --> 00:19:40.220
Be careful, please.

00:19:42.222 --> 00:19:45.142
I am not saving someone who will not say thank you.

00:19:45.225 --> 00:19:46.643
You're still on that?

00:20:27.935 --> 00:20:29.227
My baby.

00:20:45.577 --> 00:20:48.372
You know how to shoot a bow?

00:20:48.455 --> 00:20:51.166
Everyone tried to stop me because I'm a princess,

00:20:51.250 --> 00:20:53.502
But I stubbornly insisted my father teach me.

00:20:53.585 --> 00:20:55.837
So you have been peculiar since you were little.

00:20:56.546 --> 00:20:59.466
I will spin thread from the shirt made by the Favored Court Lady,

00:20:59.549 --> 00:21:01.134
And stain it with my blood.

00:21:01.927 --> 00:21:04.638
If you wrap this thread around an arrow and hit the spirit,

00:21:04.721 --> 00:21:06.473
It can weaken its resentment.

00:21:07.724 --> 00:21:08.976
Here.

00:21:11.353 --> 00:21:14.982
When the baby's crying stops, that is when you shoot.

00:21:17.526 --> 00:21:20.779
We must release the resentment born of being falsely accused,

00:21:20.862 --> 00:21:23.198
As well as the grief of losing her child.

00:22:00.694 --> 00:22:02.362
Killing those of royal blood

00:22:02.863 --> 00:22:04.489
Will not bring you your child back to you.

00:22:05.073 --> 00:22:08.869
So release your resentment now, and go to the afterlife.

00:22:08.952 --> 00:22:12.414
Free yourself from this hell of a palace, now!

00:22:48.742 --> 00:22:51.661
Your Royal Highness, Prince Yeongan has awakened.

00:22:51.745 --> 00:22:53.121
What?

00:22:55.165 --> 00:22:57.542
Are you saying he's shown signs of improvement?

00:22:57.626 --> 00:23:01.505
Not merely signs of improvement. He is said to have recovered completely.

00:23:01.588 --> 00:23:04.591
It seems that the feng shui master His Majesty had brought in

00:23:04.674 --> 00:23:06.718
Has eliminated the pond spirit.

00:23:10.055 --> 00:23:11.223
Your Majesty.

00:23:16.978 --> 00:23:19.856
Father. I am better, Father.

00:23:25.404 --> 00:23:26.446
You are.

00:23:35.122 --> 00:23:39.418
So he finally put an end to the curse that lasted 30 years?

00:23:43.713 --> 00:23:44.756
But

00:23:47.634 --> 00:23:49.553
That feng shui master

00:23:50.637 --> 00:23:53.432
How did he prove that the pond spirit is gone?

00:23:54.933 --> 00:23:57.227
I am not sure, Your Royal Highness.

00:23:57.310 --> 00:23:59.437
In the process of eliminating the spirit,

00:23:59.521 --> 00:24:03.275
He must have learned what the spirit's true identity was,

00:24:04.609 --> 00:24:06.528
And now that man knows the secret.

00:24:06.611 --> 00:24:10.031
He knows the truth behind how that lowly wench turned into a won-gwi.

00:24:11.032 --> 00:24:14.369
That man must be silenced at once.

00:24:21.835 --> 00:24:24.337
The pond spirit has finally been eliminated, Father.

00:24:26.590 --> 00:24:27.632
Yes.

00:24:29.676 --> 00:24:31.303
It does seem that way.

00:24:31.386 --> 00:24:33.597
I have now completed your orders.

00:24:34.097 --> 00:24:36.016
So I am entitled to a reward.

00:24:44.357 --> 00:24:45.567
Before that

00:25:03.710 --> 00:25:04.836
Father.

00:25:05.712 --> 00:25:07.380
The palace frightens me.

00:25:07.464 --> 00:25:08.673
Frightens you?

00:25:08.757 --> 00:25:11.593
And who would ever dare to frighten a princess?

00:25:12.719 --> 00:25:15.555
I keep hearing strange sounds everywhere I go.

00:25:17.891 --> 00:25:19.893
Saeng-gang, come over here.

00:25:22.229 --> 00:25:24.439
Here. Carry this with you.

00:25:24.523 --> 00:25:27.609
And if you do, this bell will drive away

00:25:28.235 --> 00:25:30.737
All of those strange sounds you are currently hearing.

00:25:39.079 --> 00:25:41.081
He lives because of you.

00:25:42.290 --> 00:25:43.333
Thank you.

00:25:48.672 --> 00:25:51.508
I did not do this to be praised like a child by you.

00:25:54.678 --> 00:25:55.679
Very well.

00:25:57.264 --> 00:25:59.224
Then the reward you desire.

00:25:59.808 --> 00:26:01.017
What would you like?

00:26:01.101 --> 00:26:03.436
Allow Gu-cheon the honor of leaving the palace immediately.

00:26:04.980 --> 00:26:06.564
Of course I will allow it. Yes.

00:26:06.648 --> 00:26:08.024
And do not harm him at all.

00:26:08.858 --> 00:26:11.736
That is my humble request to you, Your Majesty.

00:26:21.496 --> 00:26:23.581
Why are you not packing your things?

00:26:24.124 --> 00:26:27.210
I, uh, have nothing worth packing.

00:26:27.294 --> 00:26:28.920
I only need the jujube wood.

00:26:33.300 --> 00:26:36.553
For someone leaving the palace, you do not look very cheerful.

00:26:37.596 --> 00:26:38.680
It's just

00:26:41.349 --> 00:26:43.143
Something feels wrong.

00:26:44.728 --> 00:26:45.895
What do you mean?

00:26:46.605 --> 00:26:48.732
Has Prince Yeongan truly recovered?

00:26:48.815 --> 00:26:50.150
Is he completely well?

00:26:50.692 --> 00:26:52.235
That is what I was told.

00:26:53.278 --> 00:26:55.739
How about your wound? How is that?

00:26:56.990 --> 00:26:58.658
The pain is gone at least.

00:27:00.201 --> 00:27:01.328
What is the matter?

00:27:03.038 --> 00:27:05.707
It should not have been destroyed so easily.

00:27:06.416 --> 00:27:08.335
It was a won-gwi that had killed the princes

00:27:08.418 --> 00:27:10.170
Of the East Palace for 30 years.

00:27:10.253 --> 00:27:13.631
Four of the late King's sons, and three of the present king's sons.

00:27:14.507 --> 00:27:16.509
For a won-gwi that killed seven,

00:27:17.636 --> 00:27:19.596
Its power was far too weak.

00:27:21.431 --> 00:27:22.974
Are you really sure

00:27:24.768 --> 00:27:27.312
That the princes were killed by the pond spirit alone?

00:27:27.937 --> 00:27:31.775
If it wasn't the actions of the spirit, what's responsible?

00:27:35.945 --> 00:27:36.863
I don't know.

00:27:37.822 --> 00:27:40.325
I mean, I thought it would be a life-or-death struggle.

00:27:42.077 --> 00:27:45.205
But seeing how easily it was resolved is making me doubtful.

00:27:46.456 --> 00:27:47.666
I must be out of my mind.

00:27:47.749 --> 00:27:49.584
Completely out of my mind.

00:27:50.877 --> 00:27:54.089
Since you are departing, will you go to the temple?

00:27:54.172 --> 00:27:55.799
As if I would.

00:27:56.508 --> 00:27:58.718
I'm honestly still thinking about where to go.

00:28:00.637 --> 00:28:02.305
And what will you do, Your Highness?

00:28:02.389 --> 00:28:04.724
Have you found the one responsible for your mother's death?

00:28:08.520 --> 00:28:10.397
There is just one person it could be.

00:28:33.002 --> 00:28:37.048
Are you not the daughter of the banished Third Senior Consort Han?

00:28:37.132 --> 00:28:39.467
What brings you all the way here?

00:28:40.093 --> 00:28:42.595
I have brought a gift to celebrate Your Majesty,

00:28:42.679 --> 00:28:44.305
For your 70th birthday.

00:28:45.682 --> 00:28:48.351
It's quite modest compared to the other offerings.

00:28:49.185 --> 00:28:51.438
You came all this way for nothing, then.

00:28:52.939 --> 00:28:56.651
I never once permitted you to enter the palace.

00:28:56.735 --> 00:28:58.778
It was Father that granted permission.

00:28:58.862 --> 00:29:02.407
If that's true, he did so without my consultation?

00:29:02.490 --> 00:29:05.243
Your mother was sent away for committing a crime.

00:29:05.326 --> 00:29:06.995
You mean you framed my mother

00:29:07.078 --> 00:29:09.164
And drove her out to cover up the court maid incident

00:29:09.247 --> 00:29:10.331
In the salt storehouse.

00:29:10.415 --> 00:29:13.042
Because you feared that if that incident were to be revealed,

00:29:13.126 --> 00:29:15.670
The death of the Favored Court Lady would come to light.

00:29:15.754 --> 00:29:17.714
It's the matter tied to the pond spirit.

00:29:17.797 --> 00:29:19.924
One Your Majesty may wish to keep concealed.

00:29:26.347 --> 00:29:30.810
So you barge in spouting nothing but absurd nonsense in front of me.

00:29:30.894 --> 00:29:32.896
Your mother was banished.

00:29:33.396 --> 00:29:35.774
She was banished for burying a cursed object

00:29:35.857 --> 00:29:37.275
And because she refused to confess--

00:29:37.358 --> 00:29:39.778
Is that why you had my mother killed back then?

00:29:42.447 --> 00:29:45.825
Was her begging my father for help over and over before she died

00:29:46.367 --> 00:29:49.120
What brought up the fear of exposing your buried sins?

00:29:50.288 --> 00:29:52.665
And that poor woman's curse of the serpent's shed skin.

00:29:52.749 --> 00:29:55.335
Is it because you were raised so lowly outside the palace,

00:29:55.418 --> 00:29:57.712
Or your mother's origins perchance?

00:29:58.546 --> 00:30:00.632
You have truly lost your mind, child,

00:30:00.715 --> 00:30:04.010
Sitting there, daring to slander me with such delusions!

00:30:06.638 --> 00:30:08.306
You may open the gift.

00:30:18.274 --> 00:30:22.779
I have recreated the hangwa she received from the palace the day before she died.

00:30:30.829 --> 00:30:33.790
Not only the taste, but also the ingredients are the same.

00:30:34.624 --> 00:30:35.833
You may try it.

00:30:58.815 --> 00:31:02.735
Who on earth told you lies about such a story?

00:31:02.819 --> 00:31:04.696
I had no hand in your mother's death,

00:31:04.779 --> 00:31:06.823
Nor in the death of the Favored Court Lady.

00:31:07.323 --> 00:31:10.618
How could you possibly know events from long ago?

00:31:13.246 --> 00:31:16.875
Was it that feng shui master Gu-cheon who told you all of this?

00:31:17.584 --> 00:31:21.546
I should have taught that bastard the palace's lesson sooner.

00:31:21.629 --> 00:31:25.800
That those who dare to spread lies, here within these very walls,

00:31:27.260 --> 00:31:28.928
Will soon be dead.

00:31:36.311 --> 00:31:39.606
Tell me about the pond ghost and what you've learned about it.

00:31:39.689 --> 00:31:40.899
A ghost?

00:31:41.399 --> 00:31:42.567
In a pond?

00:31:42.650 --> 00:31:45.695
Are you talking about your grandfather who drowned in the bath?

00:31:49.991 --> 00:31:51.618
Throw him into the wooden chest.

00:31:59.125 --> 00:32:02.086
Death is the only fate for liars in this strict palace.

00:32:02.170 --> 00:32:04.047
Just like your mother in the end.

00:32:04.130 --> 00:32:05.757
She was put to a stop.

00:32:08.468 --> 00:32:09.636
I remit

00:32:10.803 --> 00:32:12.639
Those very words to you.

00:32:18.895 --> 00:32:22.315
This is the baby shirt made by the Most Favored Lady of the Court.

00:32:22.815 --> 00:32:25.902
You gave it to the royal guard and forced him to falsely claim

00:32:25.985 --> 00:32:27.528
The child as his own.

00:32:28.237 --> 00:32:30.114
-What is this? -Your Royal Highness.

00:32:30.198 --> 00:32:33.660
I know the Favored Court Lady was smeared by your lies

00:32:34.577 --> 00:32:37.747
And how you managed to have the royal bloodline all but eliminated.

00:32:37.830 --> 00:32:40.583
The late King's bloodline, you say?

00:32:41.167 --> 00:32:43.127
That lowly maid who decided she wanted to dance

00:32:43.211 --> 00:32:44.253
With a mere royal guard?

00:32:44.337 --> 00:32:45.463
Why go that far?

00:32:45.546 --> 00:32:48.299
Unlike the other concubines who received the King's favor,

00:32:49.175 --> 00:32:50.468
Why did you frame and kill her?

00:32:50.551 --> 00:32:51.803
Could it be that you were

00:32:55.223 --> 00:32:56.849
Jealous of a mere maid, Your Highness?

00:33:03.022 --> 00:33:04.357
Jealous?

00:33:11.239 --> 00:33:13.074
Did you say I was jealous?

00:33:13.658 --> 00:33:17.245
That I harbored jealousy toward such a lowborn girl?

00:33:20.039 --> 00:33:22.125
She once lived as my family's servant.

00:33:22.208 --> 00:33:24.544
I was the one who allowed her to serve in the palace

00:33:24.627 --> 00:33:28.131
As a menial labor maid, and you think I was jealous?

00:33:28.214 --> 00:33:30.007
Is that what you're saying?

00:33:35.346 --> 00:33:40.768
Unlike you, I hail from a noble lineage spanning generations!

00:33:41.352 --> 00:33:43.354
For years on end,

00:33:44.272 --> 00:33:46.899
I endured the late King's scorn and neglect

00:33:46.983 --> 00:33:49.777
For failing to bear a child for him.

00:33:49.861 --> 00:33:53.114
The fact that a lowly maidservant received His Majesty's love

00:33:53.197 --> 00:33:57.076
And could carry his child, I could not accept it!

00:33:58.494 --> 00:34:00.371
I could allow daughters of the noble households

00:34:00.455 --> 00:34:03.291
And their children, but I could never allow

00:34:03.374 --> 00:34:07.128
For that lowly, feeble woman to carry his child.

00:34:07.211 --> 00:34:12.133
She had to be eliminated by any means necessary at all.

00:34:14.177 --> 00:34:16.554
Is that why you made all those false claims then?

00:34:16.637 --> 00:34:18.389
Yeah!

00:34:18.890 --> 00:34:24.937
I had that slut tortured, then I myself killed the filthy blood

00:34:25.021 --> 00:34:27.356
That continued to grow inside her!

00:34:32.487 --> 00:34:33.780
Your Majesty.

00:34:39.619 --> 00:34:41.162
I heard you clearly.

00:34:41.746 --> 00:34:45.208
Your confession that you killed the Favored Court Lady

00:34:46.083 --> 00:34:47.585
And eliminated the King's son.

00:34:49.504 --> 00:34:51.631
What? What?

00:34:51.714 --> 00:34:54.884
I will make this public before Father and all the other ministers.

00:34:57.011 --> 00:34:58.721
You stated to me earlier

00:34:58.805 --> 00:35:02.058
That liars meet their timely death in the palace.

00:35:03.851 --> 00:35:06.437
Tell me, Your Royal Highness,

00:35:07.105 --> 00:35:09.065
What would death mean to you?

00:35:09.148 --> 00:35:12.276
It would be losing the palace and everything that defines you.

00:35:14.987 --> 00:35:17.031
The home you have lived in all your life.

00:35:17.115 --> 00:35:19.826
The power you've enjoyed for many years.

00:35:20.660 --> 00:35:21.911
I'll make sure it's all gone.

00:35:23.496 --> 00:35:24.622
Your Majesty.

00:35:25.873 --> 00:35:29.627
And what could someone like you

00:35:29.710 --> 00:35:31.629
Possibly do?

00:35:32.255 --> 00:35:37.134
Who would ever believe the words of a lowborn expelled from the palace?

00:35:37.218 --> 00:35:38.344
Who?!

00:35:40.263 --> 00:35:41.514
That much I know.

00:35:43.099 --> 00:35:45.101
Who would listen to the mere words

00:35:45.726 --> 00:35:47.019
Of the lost princess?

00:35:56.487 --> 00:36:00.825
Your Majesty, I believe your voice was loud enough for everyone to hear.

00:36:02.368 --> 00:36:03.286
Now,

00:36:05.037 --> 00:36:06.414
The time has come

00:36:06.914 --> 00:36:10.293
For you to kill these women the same as you did before.

00:36:13.713 --> 00:36:15.798
You will need a lot of jars for their bones.

00:36:17.174 --> 00:36:18.259
Let us go.

00:36:33.441 --> 00:36:35.067
Your Majesty!

00:36:35.610 --> 00:36:37.361
Your Majesty!

00:36:43.701 --> 00:36:45.870
I cannot keep my eyes off you for a second.

00:36:45.953 --> 00:36:48.164
Why are you lying in there, beaten to a pulp?

00:36:59.425 --> 00:37:01.969
What trouble did you cause today

00:37:02.511 --> 00:37:04.972
To make Her Majesty want you dead?

00:37:06.766 --> 00:37:08.684
Was it not ordered by the King?

00:37:09.393 --> 00:37:12.188
To see if I'm capable of keeping my mouth shut or not?

00:37:14.315 --> 00:37:15.816
Since you believe that,

00:37:16.400 --> 00:37:19.070
It would be pointless to mention that is not true.

00:37:22.698 --> 00:37:24.533
Then why do you spare me?

00:37:26.911 --> 00:37:31.290
The princess earnestly pleaded with His Majesty

00:37:31.374 --> 00:37:33.334
To let you leave the palace unscathed.

00:37:34.543 --> 00:37:37.129
She must have foreseen something like this.

00:37:45.179 --> 00:37:46.764
This is your pass to leave the palace.

00:37:49.767 --> 00:37:51.352
And your compensation.

00:37:53.437 --> 00:37:54.939
Watch your mouth out there.

00:37:55.022 --> 00:37:58.192
All eight provinces of Joseon lie in the hand of His Majesty.

00:38:22.967 --> 00:38:25.303
They do not let me go easily.

00:38:28.431 --> 00:38:30.349
Still, it's over now.

00:38:35.229 --> 00:38:36.188
Ah

00:39:06.719 --> 00:39:08.137
I saw nothing.

00:39:08.220 --> 00:39:10.222
Nothing at all. I did not see anything.

00:39:18.522 --> 00:39:19.398
Ah no!

00:39:32.745 --> 00:39:34.872
Whoa, whoa.

00:39:41.879 --> 00:39:44.799
I have repaid the debt I owed you for saving me.

00:39:46.133 --> 00:39:47.134
So take care.

00:40:09.115 --> 00:40:11.325
I'll give you a bit of my yang energy.

00:40:11.992 --> 00:40:14.120
Just enough for your body to recover.

00:40:21.710 --> 00:40:22.711
Get off!

00:40:22.795 --> 00:40:23.879
Let go!

00:40:23.963 --> 00:40:26.173
Don't take too much, damn it. That's enough!

00:40:53.033 --> 00:40:54.410
You do not look well.

00:40:55.744 --> 00:40:56.787
Perhaps you are ill?

00:40:58.080 --> 00:41:02.168
It's been hard on me, I think, working alongside Gu-cheon lately.

00:41:03.377 --> 00:41:04.795
And considering the part you played

00:41:04.879 --> 00:41:07.298
At the Queen Dowager's quarters last night,

00:41:08.090 --> 00:41:09.675
It makes perfect sense.

00:41:09.758 --> 00:41:13.179
And the Queen Dowager, do you plan to do anything about her?

00:41:14.346 --> 00:41:17.349
Is that why you wanted to talk this early in the morning?

00:41:17.433 --> 00:41:18.350
No.

00:41:18.434 --> 00:41:21.187
I wanted to make sure Gu-cheon made it out all right

00:41:21.270 --> 00:41:22.897
And is free of the palace.

00:41:26.609 --> 00:41:28.527
You fret too easily.

00:41:29.820 --> 00:41:34.283
He will have left the palace by now and surely will have traveled far already.

00:41:34.366 --> 00:41:36.911
After all, he saved my son.

00:41:38.996 --> 00:41:41.415
I have no desire to hurt Gu-cheon.

00:41:42.708 --> 00:41:44.793
He saved my child from death.

00:41:46.670 --> 00:41:48.088
Do not be worried.

00:41:50.299 --> 00:41:52.259
I must say, though,

00:41:52.343 --> 00:41:56.013
I did not expect him to deal with the pond spirit so easily.

00:41:58.265 --> 00:42:01.310
Indeed, Father. Even Gu-cheon felt strange about it.

00:42:01.393 --> 00:42:04.688
He questioned whether it was truly the pond spirit that killed the princes.

00:42:07.024 --> 00:42:08.025
Father

00:42:09.902 --> 00:42:13.113
I want to know about the late King's first son, the Crown Prince.

00:42:13.197 --> 00:42:14.657
How exactly did he pass away?

00:42:20.246 --> 00:42:21.830
Your Royal Highness!

00:42:23.249 --> 00:42:24.542
Your Royal Highness!

00:42:24.625 --> 00:42:26.961
Summon the physician!

00:42:27.044 --> 00:42:28.087
The physician!

00:42:29.755 --> 00:42:32.091
The Crown Prince Your Royal Highness.

00:42:38.472 --> 00:42:39.765
A curse.

00:42:43.978 --> 00:42:46.522
He passed away because a spirit had cursed him.

00:42:48.023 --> 00:42:49.942
What of the late King's second son?

00:43:08.168 --> 00:43:09.837
A spirit killed him.

00:43:10.879 --> 00:43:13.966
The third and fourth brothers as well. All four of them.

00:43:18.721 --> 00:43:20.472
Are you really sure

00:43:20.556 --> 00:43:23.475
That the princes were killed by the pond spirit alone?

00:43:29.857 --> 00:43:31.275
What is the matter?

00:43:35.237 --> 00:43:38.824
Your Majesty. The hunting preparations are complete.

00:43:38.907 --> 00:43:40.909
Prince Yeongan is waiting for you.

00:43:41.493 --> 00:43:42.494
Very well.

00:43:47.958 --> 00:43:49.501
We will continue this later.

00:44:39.843 --> 00:44:42.471
We cannot allow him to learn the truth of the pond spirit.

00:44:42.554 --> 00:44:45.641
-Stop. I don't wanna hear it. -You do not need to know either.

00:44:45.724 --> 00:44:48.435
I do not want to know any more.

00:44:48.519 --> 00:44:49.520
Please, someone

00:44:49.603 --> 00:44:50.979
Admitted to the crime

00:44:51.063 --> 00:44:53.440
-Help me. -Your father is the palace entity.

00:44:59.363 --> 00:45:00.698
Why are you crying?

00:45:01.365 --> 00:45:02.991
More importantly, why haven't you left yet?

00:45:03.075 --> 00:45:04.952
There's one thing I didn't see.

00:45:05.536 --> 00:45:07.788
The spirit that cursed Prince Yeongan

00:45:07.871 --> 00:45:09.665
Was not the Favored Court Lady.

00:45:11.250 --> 00:45:13.252
The one that tore your body and soul was not her.

00:45:13.335 --> 00:45:14.670
There's got to be another.

00:45:15.379 --> 00:45:16.213
Then, um

00:45:18.298 --> 00:45:20.384
Who was the one that tried to kill

00:45:21.176 --> 00:45:22.553
Crown Prince Yeongan?

00:45:37.192 --> 00:45:39.194
I will have my revenge.

00:45:40.112 --> 00:45:41.196
The King

00:45:42.656 --> 00:45:45.659
Must pay for the sins that he has committed.

00:45:49.288 --> 00:45:52.291
The secrets of the royal house will be revealed.

00:45:52.791 --> 00:45:53.667
And I

00:45:55.210 --> 00:45:57.379
I will become the real one.

00:46:00.340 --> 00:46:04.219
I will wipe out the royal bloodline!

00:47:24.800 --> 00:47:27.302
Prince Yeongan. We need to go find Prince Yeongan!

00:47:27.803 --> 00:47:28.637
Wait.

00:47:29.304 --> 00:47:30.305
It's already too late.

00:47:45.863 --> 00:47:48.031
Is there a royal physician back there?

00:47:48.699 --> 00:47:50.617
Send for the royal physician!

00:47:51.660 --> 00:47:52.536
Take formation.

00:47:52.619 --> 00:47:55.956
Stay calm, everyone. Don't break formation.

00:47:56.790 --> 00:47:58.000
Secure the perimeter.

00:47:58.083 --> 00:48:00.210
-What's happening? -Protect His Majesty!

00:48:03.714 --> 00:48:05.674
Then you should leave the palace through this path.

00:48:05.757 --> 00:48:06.633
You must run away now.

00:48:06.717 --> 00:48:08.927
Since you were unable to save his son,

00:48:09.428 --> 00:48:11.555
He will find you and kill you immediately.

00:48:12.055 --> 00:48:13.473
But if I leave you behind,

00:48:14.474 --> 00:48:16.727
You will die the same as Prince Yeongan.

00:48:20.772 --> 00:48:23.191
-That is a matter beyond your concern. -It does concern me.

00:48:23.775 --> 00:48:25.277
You saved my life.

00:48:25.360 --> 00:48:27.821
You risked everything coming to the other realm to save me,

00:48:27.904 --> 00:48:31.325
And now this time, I'll be the one who is going to save you.

